updatedByUserId.description: The user ID of the user who initiated the property update.

timestamp.description: The date and time when the property update occurred.

property.description: The specific property that was updated in the company record.

companyId.description: The unique identifier of the company to which the property history record belongs.

sourceType.description: The type of the source that updated the property in the company record.

sourceId.description: The identifier of the source that updated the property in the company record.

value.description: The new value of the property after the update.

archived.description: Flag indicating if the company property history record is archived or not.
